x.delay: delay(ctx) { if (ctx.type !== 'data' || ctx.xStarted) { return 0; } const totalDuration = 10000; const delayBetweenPoints = totalDuration / 1000; ctx.xStarted = true; return ctx.index * delayBetweenPoints; }

y.delay: (ctx) => { if (ctx.type !== 'data' || ctx.yStarted) { return 0; } const totalDuration = 10000; const delayBetweenPoints = totalDuration / 1000; ctx.yStarted = true; return ctx.index * delayBetweenPoints; }
